    public class AssociationTuplePmmlAnalyticOutputDataMapper
extends TuplePmmlAnalyticOutputDataMapper
    An TuplePmmlAnalyticOutputDataMapper that can map the output of a PMML model evaluation of an Association model to a Tuple. Since it requires special output mapping as no output fields are created in the model.
